    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="初始化hexo"><a href="#初始化hexo" class="headerlink" title="初始化hexo"></a>初始化hexo</h2><p>  hexo init</p><h2 id="本地启动"><a href="#本地启动" class="headerlink" title="本地启动"></a>本地启动</h2><p>  hexo s</p><h2 id="新建文章"><a href="#新建文章" class="headerlink" title="新建文章"></a>新建文章</h2><p>  hexo n ‘title’</p><h2 id="清理what"><a href="#清理what" class="headerlink" title="清理what"></a>清理what</h2><p>  hexo clean </p><h2 id="生成"><a href="#生成" class="headerlink" title="生成"></a>生成</h2><p>  hexo g(generate) </p><p>npm i hexo-deployer-git –save  这是干嘛用的</p><h2 id="配置-config-yml"><a href="#配置-config-yml" class="headerlink" title="配置_config.yml"></a>配置_config.yml</h2><p>deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repository: <a href="https://github.com/Jaime0108/Jaime0108.github.io.git">https://github.com/Jaime0108/Jaime0108.github.io.git</a><br>  branch: main</p><h2 id="修改主题"><a href="#修改主题" class="headerlink" title="修改主题"></a>修改主题</h2><p>  1.下载主题: git clone <a href="https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git">https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git</a> themes&#x2F;yilia<br>  2.修改_config.yml theme配置</p><h2 id="部署到远端"><a href="#部署到远端" class="headerlink" title="部署到远端"></a>部署到远端</h2><p>  hexo d</p><p><a href="https://jaime0108.github.io/">https://jaime0108.github.io/</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
